stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Created
    Created --> Seeded: initial reserve composition
    Seeded --> Active: market enabled
    Active --> PartiallyDisabled: asset flags changed
    Active --> Paused: emergency pause
    PartiallyDisabled --> Active: flags restored
    PartiallyDisabled --> Deprecated: asset no longer supported
    Paused --> Active: unpause
    Paused --> Deprecated
    Deprecated --> [*]
